BO - Design - Image Settings - Check product image format Steps    Step Description Expected result     * Go to BO &gt; Design &gt; Image settings
* Scroll down to have image generation option * JPEG/PNG should be checked * You can&rsquo;t unchecked the JPEG/PNG format
* Base format should be : &ldquo;Use PNG only if the base image is in PNG format&rdquo;   Check the checkboxes next to Webp The checkbox should be checked and the Webp is enabled   * Go to Catalog &gt; Product * Click on &ldquo;Add new product&rdquo;

